<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stop-n">stop <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stɒp/    美 /stɑːp/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>停止；中止：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>without a stop
不停地</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>停车站：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Where is the nearest bus stop?
最近的公共汽车站在哪儿？</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>标点 (尤指句号)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Put a (full) stop at the end of the sentence.
在句末加上句号。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="bring-to-a-stop">bring ... to a stop</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使…停下来：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The accident brought the traffic to a complete stop.
这起事故使交通完全中断了。</p></div>

<h3 id="come-to-a-stop">come to a stop</h3>
<p>1.<strong>停止：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He came to such a sudden stop that we almost hit him.
他突然停了下来，我们差点撞上他。</p></div></div>